<h4 id="iterator_property_map">iterator_property_map</h4>
<p>This is an adaptor that wraps a type that models <em>RandomAccessIterator</em> to
create an <em>LValuePropertyMap</em>.</p>
<ol>
  <li>This adaptor is often useful for creating a property map out of an array,
where the key is an integer offset into the array, and the array contains
value objects.</li>
  <li>You need to provide a property map that converts from the the key type to an
integer if the key type is not an integer.</li>
</ol>

<div class="language-cpp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="cp">#include &lt;iostream&gt;
#include &lt;boost/property_map.hpp&gt;
</span>	<span class="kt">double</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">[]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mf">4.5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.9</span><span class="p">};</span>
	<span class="n">boost</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">iterator_property_map</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="kt">double</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">boost</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">identity_property_map</span><span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">pmap</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">);</span>
	<span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">"property map: "</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">boost</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pmap</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>
	<span class="n">boost</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">put</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pmap</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">1.9</span><span class="p">);</span>
	<span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="s">"property map: "</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">boost</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pmap</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">std</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

